name: Aline dress
description: This dress basically follows the Aline silhouette â€“ ie flowy from the shoulders. It can also have a fitted defined waist but the hem is always flared giving the whole silhouette the shape of a capital letter A.

name: Tent dress
description: A shapeless tentlike full dress,  that hangs loosely from the shoulders; it has a baggy silhouette and is usually worn short. The airy billowy dress is a favorite as a summer wear.

name: Yoke dress
description: This is a type of dress with a shaped top portion of the bodice which is separate from the bodice. The yoked dress can have a front yoke or back yoke or both

name: Empire
description: This is a  high waist dress that has a fitting bodice till just under the bust and then a flowy silhouette

name: Shift dress
description: This is a short sleeveless dress  that skims the body without a fitted waist.

name: Dirndl dress
description: This is a European traditional dress originally worn by peasants there;The dress has an apron with lacing on the back or front.

name: Sheath dress
description: A close fitting dress usually ending near the knee. Usually there will be a slit in the back so that you can walk comfortably.

name: drop waist dress
description: This is a loose fitting dress with the skirt seam being somewhere near the hip rather than at the waist length.

name: Tunic dress
description: This is a loose fitting dress ending near the hips  or near the knee , usually with slits on the side seams.

name: Princess seam dress
description: This is a dress with a princess seam down the bodice.

name: Blouson dress
description: This is a dress with a fitted/clinched waist which will cause the top portion to have a billowing effect.

name: Shirt waist dress
description: This kind of dress resembles a shirt in the top portion, with a collar and an open front button placket.

name: Wrap around dress
description: This is a style of dress with an Asymmetrical closing. This  dress usually has one side wrapped over the other side and usually has a tie which closes the front opening.

name: Peasant Dress
description: This is a dress originally worn by the peasants in Europe, with raglan sleeves or very loose sleeves.

name: Baby doll dress
description: A baby doll dress refers to a short sweet dress with a fitted bodice ( at times a bralette) and a loose gathered skirt. This is usually is used as a nightgown.

name: Body con dress
description: This refers to a tight fitting body hugging dress made of a stretchy fabric. It usually ends near or above the knee.

name: Cocktail dress
description: This is a short dressy dress meant for attending semi-formal functions.

name: Debutante dress
description: This is a white gown typically worn by debutantes on their first ball. The white formal full length gown is usually accompanied by white kid gloves.

name: Skater dress
description: This is a dress that has a fitted bodice and a very flared circular skirt. They have an Aline silhouette with a very defined waist.

name: Camisole dress
description: This dress resembles the camisole worn as a slip or nightgown. A camisole dress is a longer version of this and is usually worn over tops.

name: Pinafore dress
description: This is a collarless, sleeveless low cut dress which is worn over tops / blouses.

name: Granny dress
description: A granny dress is a loose fitting dress with long sleeves. This dress usually has ruffles or flounces and a high collar.

name: Harem dress
description: This is a full length dress with a flared cut narrowing down to a narrower hem. It is usually made in a flowy fabric.

name: Trumpet dress
description: A  trumpet dress has a fitted bodice till the knee or just below the knee  where it flares to the hem.

name: Sweater dress
description: A sweater dress is a long sweater that can be worn on its own as a dress. It is usually knee length.
